.TH wxTaskBarIconEvent 3 "wx 2.5.4" "Ericsson AB" "Erlang Module Definition"
.SH NAME
wxTaskBarIconEvent \- The event class used by \fIwxTaskBarIcon\fR.

.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
For a list of the event macros meant to be used with \fIwxTaskBarIconEvent\fR, please look at \fIwxTaskBarIcon\fR description.

.PP
This class is derived, and can use functions, from:


.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
\h'-04'\(bu\h'+03'\c
.\}
.el \{\
.sp -1
.IP \(bu 2.3
.\}.PP
\fIwxEvent\fR

.RE

.PP
wxWidgets docs: wxTaskBarIconEvent

